data.description: Acadian style stucco house located on the circular drive of W Adams Court. High arched ceilings featuring exposed wood beams in the spacious living area. Open dining room just off the updated kitchen. One full bathroom located on the first floor and a balcony off the primary suite over looks the den. Large fenced in backyard with a small patio area.
